wikipedia_page.main: Everard (or Everard of Calne; died probably 1146)  was a medieval Bishop of Norwich.

response: | Also possibly known as Everard of Calne. Formerly Archdeacon of Salisbury. Elected bishop soon after 13 March 1121 and consecrated on 12 June 1121. Resigned in 1145 and died on 12 October 1146
